definitions.definition: A pouch or cavity in a bone or other tissue , especially one in the bones of the face or skull connecting with the nasal cavities ( the paranasal sinus ) .
An irregular venous or lymphatic cavity , reservoir , or dilated vessel .

subdefinitions.definition: Relating to or denoting the sinoatrial node of the heart or its function of regulating the heartbeat .

definitions.definition: An abnormal cavity or passage such as a fistula , leading from a deep-seated infection and discharging pus to the surface.
A rounded notch or depression between two lobes or teeth in the margin of a leaf or petal .
A bay of the sea ; a recess in the shore .
